"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10013064\">",
"      How do I store and/or throw out this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10013065\">",
"      General drug facts",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"   </ul>",
"  </div>",
