" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Progression of erosions with gold therapy in rheumatoid arthritis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 421px; height: 338px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Changes in erosion score in hand X-ray of patients RA who were randomized to therapy with myocrisin, auranofin, or placebo. Patients in both gold groups showed clinical improvement by articular index, grip strength, and morning stiffness. However, these clinical benefits were not confirmed by the hand radiograph erosion score which showed a deterioration in many patients.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from Capell, HA, Lewis, D, Carey, J, Ann Rheum Dis 1986; 45:705.",
"    </div>",
